archive: ZIP archive containing files for a FLASH problem (Config, Makefile, F90).

auto: Enable setup to generate a 'rough draft' of a Units file (-auto).
ed_maxPulseSections: Maximum number of sections per laser pulse (ed_maxPulseSections).
hdf5typeio: Use  hdf5 with parallel io capability for compatible binary IO output (+hdf5typeio).
laser: Use source terms for energy deposition (+laser).
maxblocks: Maximum number of blocks per process (maxblocks).
mgd: Use the MGD (magneto gas dynamic) radiative transfermodule (+mgd).
mgd_meshgroups: mgd meshgroups * meshCopyCount sets the MAXIMUM number of radiation groups that can be used in a simulation (mgd_meshgroups).
mtmmmt: Use the MultiTemp/MultiType and Tabulated EOSes (for HEDPsimulations) (+mtmmmt).
nofbs: Use the uniform grid in a non-fixed block size mode (+nofbs).
nxb: How many cells each block of the mesh contains (not counting guard cells) (nxb).
nyb: How many cells each block of the mesh contains (not counting guard cells) (nyb).
nzb: How many cells each block of the mesh contains (not counting guard cells) (nzb).
species: An alternative to specifying the SPECIES in the Config file.
ug: Use the uniform grid in a fixed block size mode (+ug).
usm3t: Use unsplit MHD with MultiTemp EOS (+usm3t).

vmax: Maximum limit of color bar values.
vmin: Minimum limit of color bar values.
